{"id": 2622, "genre": 1001, "title": "你觉得伴侣之间哪些地方可以不同？", "description": "合适就是求同存异，两人在哪些地方应该一致，哪些地方不同步也行？", "record_count": 3192, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20181112183353CQHTmAtM8R1hd0qp.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-11-19T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 312585, "content": "为彼此的相同惊喜，同时尊重认同彼此的不同，这是我认为两人相爱最好的状态。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1511612}, {"id": 311820, "content": "性别不同也是可以在一起的", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1507930}, {"id": 313612, "content": "三观，性格都挺重要啊，最重要的的确是和而不同了，相互包容共同进步应该是一段良好关系应有的样子", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1517165}, {"id": 311826, "content": "在自己可以忍受的方面伴侣可以与自己不同", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1352296}, {"id": 311827, "content": "能互相理解和尊重什么不同都没关系", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1502472}, {"id": 311829, "content": "性观念不同，一个开放，一个保守", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1180226}, {"id": 311830, "content": "和而不同\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1450304}, {"id": 311832, "content": "哪哪都不同", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1346244}, {"id": 312348, "content": "什么都可以不同 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1476609}, {"id": 311837, "content": "在有旁人的时候意见一致，在二人世界时候可有自己的见解有争论", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1507975}, {"id": 311838, "content": "父母", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1374119}, {"id": 311839, "content": "尺寸", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 446030}, {"id": 312095, "content": "不同的身体，不同的思维，不同的感受。人本来就是矛盾的集合体，越多的不符才有越多的相符", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1509705}, {"id": 312351, "content": "爱好可以不同，但要包容对方的爱好；\n口味可以不同，但不会强迫相同；\n爱情需要理解与包容。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1510517}, {"id": 310304, "content": "教育背景可以不同，但是得接得住对方的话茬（我是徐州工程学院的她是哥大毕业）", "image": null, "praise_count": 403, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 311840, "content": "兴趣爱好穿衣打扮这种小事上可以不一样，但是三观一致真的太重要了，和前任分手就是因为三观不一致，和现任三观真的是高度契合，对我而言找一个三观相似的人真的是太重要了，相处起来也舒服，就是所谓的默契吧❤", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1353112}, {"id": 312352, "content": "什么都可以不同，但他们必须要在同一个世界", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1510521}, {"id": 310305, "content": "爱好可以不同，但不能讨厌对方的爱好（我想听郭德纲，她要听陈奕迅）", "image": null, "praise_count": 479, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 311841, "content": "请问伴侣是好奇心日报统一发放吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1214159}, {"id": 310306, "content": "消费观可以不一样，但让一个人来管财务可以避免很多吵架（双十一究竟要不要买台戴森吸尘器）", "image": null, "praise_count": 85, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 311842, "content": "占用马桶的时间", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1198027}, {"id": 311843, "content": "以前我对伴侣的要求是，三观和我一样，后来觉得是女的最为重要，其他可以次之，再后来觉得男的都能接受了，只要有伴就好，现在想想，另一半什么的，就算了吧，一个人挺好😂。", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1404895}, {"id": 311846, "content": "高潮的感觉可以不同", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1506894}, {"id": 311847, "content": "性别可以不同，但是我一个女生有女朋友，你可以不理解，但请尊重。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 828751}, {"id": 311848, "content": "三观合", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1508048}, {"id": 311849, "content": "爱超越性别。只要谈得来，两个人都愿意多付出一些爱，没有什么问题", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1508056}, {"id": 311850, "content": "可以有各种不同，但是爱好、观念、生活习惯不应有冲突，即一个人喜欢的恰好是另一个人厌恶甚至痛恨的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1340666}, {"id": 311851, "content": "兴趣爱好不同", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1508080}, {"id": 311852, "content": "性别", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1320862}, {"id": 311853, "content": "爱好 习惯 可以不同 最重要的还是理解包容", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1490778}, {"id": 311855, "content": "是非观、笑点一致", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1114068}, {"id": 311856, "content": "脚步", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 585603}, {"id": 311857, "content": "收入不同，但是消费观要一致", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1507575}, {"id": 311858, "content": "成绩可以不同，话茬一定要相同.", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1506404}, {"id": 312627, "content": "三观一致，性格可以不相同", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1511821}, {"id": 311860, "content": "all，最大的不同就是不能有太多的相同", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 361301}, {"id": 311861, "content": "身高，体重，年龄", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1508176}, {"id": 311862, "content": "嗯嗯哦", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1508210}, {"id": 311863, "content": "思考方式", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1502555}, {"id": 311864, "content": "我觉得什么都可以不同", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1472963}, {"id": 311865, "content": "除了三观，哪里都可以不同啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1508232}, {"id": 311866, "content": "哪里都可以不一样。但希望两个人对未来的憧憬和希望是一样的！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1450211}, {"id": 311867, "content": "性格上可以互补", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1441187}, {"id": 319291, "content": "没有伴侣，这个问题超纲了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1497481}, {"id": 311868, "content": "应该一致：\n金钱观，这点分歧大的，基本没戏。\n性观念，这点分歧大的，互相伤害。\n人生观，两个人对人生的意义、追求不一样。容易一开始基于性冲动走一起，然后遵从三观的指引而分手。\n可以不同步\n思维方式：男女思维方式本来就不一样好嘛\n兴趣爱好：同化\n生活习惯：磨合\n家境：能在一起算我输", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1502607}, {"id": 311870, "content": "國籍，地域，膚色，可以不同", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1507705}, {"id": 313406, "content": "性别", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1516414}, {"id": 311872, "content": "可以接受不同", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1222366}, {"id": 311874, "content": "本来还想说点什么。 但热评已经说的差不多了耶", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 90121}, {"id": 311875, "content": "发型", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1351497}]}